show.title: The Natural Nurse

title: September 27, 2010
content:
Dr. Eugene Zampieron, ND, AHG, www.drznaturally.com, interviews Dr. Kathleen Albertson, L. <!--more--> Ac.
, Acupuncturist, Herbalist.
Dr Albertson is the author of Acupuncture and Chinese Herbal Medicine for Women’s Health: Bridging the Gap Between Western and Eastern Medicine.
Dr Albertson believes in educating patients and the public on the benefits of holistic health and bridging the gap between Western and Eastern health care.
She has been in private practice in CA for over 15 years.
While specializing in women’s health, she treats men, and children as well, of all ages, for a wide variety of heath problems.Contact: www.orangecountyacupuncture.com Phone: 949 861-8901
